snippet.title: The Alto Collection: Now on The Epic Games Store, Xbox One, PlayStation 4 & soon on Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
The Alto Collection: http://thealtocollection.com/

The Alto Collection is available now for pre-order on Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/en_CA/games/detail/the-alto-collection-switch/

The Alto Collection is coming to Nintendo Switch November 26th, 2020 and available now on The Epic Games Store, Xbox One and PlayStation 4.

For the first time ever, we have combined Alto’s Adventure and Alto’s Odyssey into one unified experience. Join Alto and friends and explore the vast, open deserts and placid ivory snows together in one collection on The Epic Games Store, Xbox One, PlayStation 4 and coming soon to Nintendo Switch.

Trailer by Pedro Cascao
Music by Fenn (Falling Up)
